WEBVTT

00:02.089 --> 00:05.124
You are being watched.

00:05.126 --> 00:07.126
The government
has a secret system--

00:07.128 --> 00:11.797
a machine that spies on you
every hour of every day.

00:11.799 --> 00:13.999
I designed the machine
to detect acts of terror,

00:14.001 --> 00:15.834
but it sees everything...

00:15.836 --> 00:18.837
Violent crimes
involving ordinary people.

00:18.839 --> 00:21.907
The government considers
these people irrelevant.

00:21.909 --> 00:23.942
We don't.

00:23.944 --> 00:28.313
Hunted by the authorities,
we work in secret.

00:28.315 --> 00:30.148
You will never find us.

00:30.150 --> 00:32.150
But victim or perpetrator,

00:32.152 --> 00:35.153
if your number's up,
we'll find you.

